<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>BSI-Meldestelle — NIS-2-Meldung</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: DejaVu Sans, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; color: #1a1a2e; }
        h1 { font-size: 14pt; border-bottom: 2px solid #d62828; padding-bottom: 6px; }
        h2 { font-size: 12pt; margin-top: 18px; color: #d62828; }
        table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-bottom: 14px; }
        th { background: #FDECEA; text-align: left; padding: 6px 8px; border: 1px solid #f5c6cb; }
        td { padding: 5px 8px; border: 1px solid #f5c6cb; vertical-align: top; }
        .label { font-weight: bold; width: 40%; }
        .footer { font-size: 8pt; color: #666; border-top: 1px solid #ccc; margin-top: 20px; padding-top: 6px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<h1>Meldung eines erheblichen Sicherheitsvorfalls — BSI-Meldestelle (NIS-2)</h1>
<p><em>An: Bundesamt für Sicherheit in der Informationstechnik (BSI) — Meldestelle</em></p>
{% if submission_contact_email %}<p><strong>Kontakt:</strong> {{ submission_contact_email }}</p>{% endif %}
{% if submission_url %}<p><strong>Portal:</strong> {{ submission_url }}</p>{% endif %}

{% if header_template %}
<blockquote>{{ header_template }}</blockquote>
{% endif %}

<h2>1. Vorfallsbeschreibung</h2>
<table>
    <tr><td class="label">Titel</td><td>{{ title }}</td></tr>
    <tr><td class="label">Schweregrad</td><td>{{ severity }}</td></tr>
    <tr><td class="label">Entdeckungsdatum</td><td>{{ detected_at ? detected_at|date('d.m.Y H:i') : '—' }}</td></tr>
    <tr><td class="label">Status</td><td>{{ status }}</td></tr>
</table>

<h2>2. Beschreibung</h2>
<table>
    <tr><td>{{ description ?? 'Keine Beschreibung hinterlegt.' }}</td></tr>
</table>

<div class="footer">
    Erstellt am: {{ generated_at|date('d.m.Y H:i') }} — Vertraulich / NIS-2-Meldung
</div>
</body>
</html>
